				"hint": "You gain the ability to twist your environment to your will. You can use Wild Shape as a bonus action, causing one effect when you do. You can use this feature twice, regaining all uses at the end of a short or long rest. When you gain this feature, you pick two of the following wild shape options. When you finish a long rest, you can exchange one of your Wild Shape options for another of the same level. All of these effects count as magical, but they are not spells."
